s from the Savage Worlds RPG</font></div><div align="justify"><div align="justify" style="text-align: center; "><font color="#111111" face="Trebuchet MS" size="2"><br></font></div><div align="justify" style="text-align: center; "><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="4" color="#8a0000">FREE STANDARD WORLDWIDE SHIPPING FOR ORDERS OVER £25.00</font></div><div align="justify" style="text-align: center; "><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="4" color="#8a0000"><br></font></div><div align="justify" style="text-align: center; "><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="4" color="#8a0000">UK ORDERS INCLUDE FREE STANDARD POST &amp; PACKING.</font></div></div></div><div align="justify" style="text-align: -webkit-left;"><font color="#111111" face="Trebuchet MS" size="2"><br></font></div></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="2"><br></font><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%" style="text-align: center;"><tbody><tr><td bgcolor="#242424"><table border="0" width="100%" cellpadding="2"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center; "><font color="#ffffff" face="Trebuchet MS" size="4">SAVAGE WORLDS</font></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" width="100%"><div align="justify" style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: -webkit-auto; "><center style="display: inline !important; "><font color="#000000" face="Trebuchet MS" size="2"><p align="center" style="display: inline !important; "><br></p></font></center></span></div><div align="justify" style="text-align: center;"><font face="Trebuchet MS" size="2">Created in partnership with Pinnacle Entertainment Group, Savage Worlds Miniatures are 25mm heroic scale white metal gaming figurines based on the creatures and personalities of the Savage Worlds Roleplaying Game. With dozens of beautiful sculpts already in production and more releasing all the time, Savage Worlds Miniatures bring the world of Savage Worlds to life on your tabletop!</font></div><div alig