</ul></div>                       <div id="listing_tab2_content" style="display:none;"><p>Chaos Cards are the leading trading card store in the United Kingdom, supplying a huge range of customers, from passionate card collectors and hobby stores to large internet catalogue firms and distribution companies.</p>
<p>We have an unbelievable range of items at fantastic prices and our customer service is second to none. So what are you waiting for! Order today and become a customer, you will not be disappointed! </p></div><div id="listing_tab3_content" style="display:none;"><p>Please contact us for more information.</p></div><div id="listing_tab4_content" style="display:none;"><h2>Shipping Times</h2>
<p>UK mainland 1st Class - usually takes 1-3 days from date of dispatch. It can take longer sometimes, for example, if your parcel is too big to fit through a letterbox, then you may have missed the delivery. Royal Mail do not always leave a calling card and it may be at the sorting office. If you parcel is more than 3 days late, we would recommend checking with neighbours and the local sorting office.</p>
<p>Delivery by courier, such as DHL or Parcelforce is tracked and the delivery time is typically 2 working days from the time of dispatch. Next day delivery service is available on request. If your parcel has not arrived within 15 working days of receiving our dispatch notice and it is not at the sorting office, then please contact us. Please provide your name as it would appear on your order, order reference and the date you received our dispatch note, this will help us to deal with your query quickly for you.</p>
<p>Airmail to Europe - Usually takes 5 -10 days, but it can take longer if there is a delay in the postage system. Please allow 28 working days for your item to arrive. Standard Airmail is not tracked. Signed for and Airsure services are available and are tracked. We also offer a flat rate Euro Parcel service to mainland Europe which is tracked, please do contact us if you are wanting to place a large order.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Your purchase is covered by the consumer Distant Selling Regulations, you may therefore cancel the order within 7 days of receiving the goods. You will receive a full refund if the order is not yet dispatched, if the order has been dispatched before you cancel, then you would be able to return the item, but would be liable for the postage charges.</p>
<p>We have a very good no quibbles return policy. If you wish to return an item you can do within 7 days of purchase, so long as the item is returned unopened and in the same condition as received. Please contact us if you wish to arrange a return. A full refund for the product is given once the items are returned, your cost of posting the item back to us and the postage paid by you when ordering is not covered by this policy.</p>
<p>Please return your goods to:</p>
<p>FTK Gaming Network Ltd (T/A Chaos Cards) </p>
<p>PO BOX 731 </p>
<p>FOLKESTONE </p>
