<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://img.auctiva.com/imgdata/3/6/0/1/4/0/webimg/336235232_o.gif" alt="" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>RENEGADE LEGION<br /></strong></span></span></span></span></em></p><p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: x-large;">LEGIONNAIRE<br /></span></span></span></span></em></p><p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: x-large;">The Role Playing Game</span></span></span></span></em></p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><em><br /></em></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><em>Published by Fasa. 1990<br /></em></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><em>Soft cover. 200 Pages<br /></em></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><em>OUT OF PRINT</em></span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><div style="text-align: center;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#ffffff"><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: small;"><em><span style="font-family: Arial;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: small;"><em>&quot;Let them hate, so long as they fear.&quot;<br />Lucius Accius</em></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></em></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></div></font></div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;">This is an RPG I''ve never heard of. But its by the same folk who brought us Shadowrun so it should be good. At the time of listing this was the only copy available in Britain, and there were only a few in the U.S, so this is uber rare.<br /></span></span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">&nbsp;</span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;">And, as a special treat for you lucky bidders, I''ve also got hold of some uber, uber rare sourcebooks, which I shall be listing. I''m too good to you!</span></span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">&nbsp;</span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;">This book is in&nbsp;&nbsp; very good condition.</span></span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">&nbsp;</span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><em><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Please check out my other listings, because if you clicked on this, I promise I will have something else to interest you!</span></span></em></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><em><br /></em></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);">&nbsp;</span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><em>SYNOPSIS</em></strong><br /></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: large;">In 6831, the battlefield is a place of push-button death and searing destruction where human courage is every bit as important as the technology. But not all battles are won on the field, and not all combat is as straightforward as a tank commander would like. Espionage, sabotage, and intrigue await players of the Renegade Legion: Legionnaire!<br /></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: large;">Renegade Legion: Legionnaire provides all the information needed to create and play a character in this ominous setting. Be a starfighter pilot, an anti-gravity tank commander, or just a free-booting adventurer in Renegade Legion: Legionnaire.</span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: large;">Renegade Legion: Legoinnaire includes material on character generation, career packages, skills, attribute points, experience, rank and fame. There are rules given for characters of alien races found within the Teeran Overlord Government (TOG), the commonwealth, and the Renegade Legions. Equipment and weapons are listed, along with individual combat rules. TOG and Commonwealth histories are presented. Shannedam County is spotlighted with planetary maps and strategic details. Here is everything you need to join the fight.</span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 255);"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: large;">IN THE BATTLE BETWEEN GOOD AND EVIL, THIS ONE COUNTS.</span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: center;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#ffffff"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: small;"><em>&quot;It is better to live one day as a tiger than a thousand years as a sheep.&quot;<br />tibetan Proverb</em></span></span></span></strong></font></div><p>&nbsp;<span style="font-size: medium;"><br /></span></p><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Impact;"><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><em><strong>SHIPPING:   UK postage is now free. Items will be sent 2nd class or via courier.   Next day delivery is also offered. If you want an item sent first class,   signed for or any other way, please contact me before paying so I can   revise the invoice.</strong></em></span></span><br /></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Impact;"><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><em><strong>Overseas   bidders will have reduced postage costs equal to the cost of UK   shipping. Please note that Standard Airmail does not have tracking   numbers. If you require a tracking number please let me know before   paying so I can adjust the invoice.</strong></em></span></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Impact;"><span style="font-family: Courier New;"><em><strong>Any   items currently for sale that have not been changed over to free   shipping, the terms and conditions on that listing will apply.</strong></em></span></span></span></span></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">&nbsp;</span></strong></div><div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><em>&nbsp; &quot;The place where you made your stand never mattered.<br />Only that you were there... and still on your feet.&quot;<br />Stephen King</em></strong></span></span></span></span></div><p style="text-align: center;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#ffffff"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><em><br /></em></strong></span></span></span></span></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p></font><br> 
